market-competition?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>随着中国电子商务巨头将目光投向海外，京东考虑收购英国电子零售商 Currys</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3252464/jdcom-considers-takeover-bid-uk-electronics-retailer-currys-chinas-e-commerce-giants-look-overseas?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>京东可能竞购英国咖喱，正值中国大型电子商务企业在国内竞争加剧和经济逆风的情况下继续寻求海外增长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 12:30:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3252464/jdcom-considers-takeover-bid-uk-electronics-retailer-currys-chinas-e-commerce-giants-look-overseas?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国科学家研制出等离子体隐形装置，使军用飞机脱离雷达</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3251401/chinese-scientists-create-plasma-stealth-device-take-military-aircraft-radar?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>研究人员开发了一种新型等离子隐形装置，可能会改变军用飞机的游戏规则。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 12:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3251401/chinese-scientists-create-plasma-stealth-device-take-military-aircraft-radar?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国敦促美国停止“无故”在边境“骚扰”中国学生</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252452/china-urges-us-stop-harassing-its-students-border-no-reason?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国公安部部长王晓红在维也纳对美国国防部长亚历杭德罗·马约卡斯表示，美国必须确保中国公民“公平入境待遇和充分尊严”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 11:00:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252452/china-urges-us-stop-harassing-its-students-border-no-reason?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国国产C919客机在新加坡展翅高飞 首次国际亮相</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3252436/chinas-home-grown-c919-passenger-jet-takes-wing-singapore-international-debut?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>备受关注的国产客机C919首次亮相国际舞台，成为新加坡航展的一大亮点。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 10:00:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3252436/chinas-home-grown-c919-passenger-jet-takes-wing-singapore-international-debut?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>魅族、OPPO 等中国智能手机厂商在 2024 年行业复苏的背景下加大了人工智能在其设备中的集成力度</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-trends/article/3252439/chinese-smartphone-vendors-meizu-oppo-step-ai-integration-their-devices-amid-expected-industry?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国手机中人工智能集成的增加表明，随着全球市场有望在 2024 年复苏，智能手机行业的新技术军备竞赛正在升温。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 09:30:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-trends/article/3252439/chinese-smartphone-vendors-meizu-oppo-step-ai-integration-their-devices-amid-expected-industry?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国未来的强国湖南希望官员“解放思想”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3252412/chinas-would-be-powerhouse-hunan-wants-officials-emancipate-their-minds?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>“平躺”政策已经结束，有效振兴全省经济的努力已经开始，这场运动针对的是各级共产党干部。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 09:00:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3252412/chinas-would-be-powerhouse-hunan-wants-officials-emancipate-their-minds?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>王毅表示，中国和西班牙同意提供“公平、非歧视”的营商环境</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252411/china-germany-should-stick-openness-and-free-trade-and-keep-policy-predictable-wang-yi-says?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>北京将取消长达24年的西班牙牛肉进口禁令，中国外交部长称这是“好消息，特别是对西班牙农民来说”。王毅在与西班牙外长阿尔瓦雷斯会谈后表示，双方同意扩大新领域合作。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 07:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252411/china-germany-should-stick-openness-and-free-trade-and-keep-policy-predictable-wang-yi-says?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>国家能源局局长表示，中国的气候目标：能源消耗不断增长、脱碳进展缓慢带来挑战</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/business/china-business/article/3252406/chinas-climate-goals-growing-energy-consumption-slow-progress-decarbonisation-pose-challenges-says?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>国家能源局（NEA）负责人表示，中国不断增长的能源消耗、脱碳进程的缓慢以及新能源装机容量的限制，对这个世界上最大的温室气体排放国的气候目标构成了重大挑战。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 06:08:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/business/china-business/article/3252406/chinas-climate-goals-growing-energy-consumption-slow-progress-decarbonisation-pose-challenges-says?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>全球影响：中国对以色列-加沙战争和红海危机的反应反映了其世界强国的哪些地位？</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3252365/global-impact-what-does-chinas-response-israel-gaza-war-and-red-sea-crisis-say-about-its-position?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在本期《全球影响》时事通讯中，我们关注北京对以色列-加沙战争和胡塞叛军袭击扰乱全球航运后的红海危机的反应。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 06:00:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3252365/global-impact-what-does-chinas-response-israel-gaza-war-and-red-sea-crisis-say-about-its-position?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中欧关系：北京在欧洲寻找机会之际，特朗普的幽灵笼罩在慕尼黑会议上</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252393/china-eu-relations-beijing-delegations-work-room-munich-conference-trump-and-nato-preoccupy?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在有关乌克兰、加沙和欧洲安全的紧张对话中，与中国有关的问题被搁置在议程中，但美国参议员表示，美国将在未来 40 年将注意力集中在东亚。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 05:00:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252393/china-eu-relations-beijing-delegations-work-room-munich-conference-trump-and-nato-preoccupy?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>香港对方便面的热爱、中国的铁路和风景：您可能错过的 5 篇周末读物</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/world/article/3252361/hong-kongs-love-affair-instant-noodles-chinas-railways-and-landscapes-captured-5-weekend-reads-you?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>从穿越中国各地的铁路到东南亚的极右景观，以下是您周末可能错过的故事。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 04:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/world/article/3252361/hong-kongs-love-affair-instant-noodles-chinas-railways-and-landscapes-captured-5-weekend-reads-you?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国领导的研究小组查明了最小的恒星及其幽灵般的孤独伴星</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3252327/china-led-research-team-pinpoints-smallest-star-and-its-ghostly-lone-companion?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>研究揭示了独特的双星系统，由一颗白矮星和一颗微小的热亚矮星组成，仅比地球大七倍。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 02:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3252327/china-led-research-team-pinpoints-smallest-star-and-its-ghostly-lone-companion?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item></channel></rss>